<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px;">
            <h1 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 25px; line-height: 30px; color: #B31885; font-weight: normal;">Une nouvelle demande de réservation a été créée.</h1>
            <ul style="padding: 0; margin: 0 0 10px 0; list-style-type: disc;">
                <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" class="list-item-first">Employé : {{AccessRequest.Employee.FullName}}</li>
                <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Date : {{formatDate AccessRequest.StartTime}}</li>
                <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Temps d'accès : {{formatTime AccessRequest.StartTime}} à {{formatTime AccessRequest.EndTime}}</li>
                <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Statut : {{AccessRequest.FrenchStatus}}</li>
                <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Immeuble / Étage : {{AccessRequest.Building.FrenchName}} - {{AccessRequest.Floor.FrenchName}}</li>
                {{#if AccessRequest.Workspace.Name}}
                    <li style="margin: 0 0 0 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">Espace de travail : {{AccessRequest.Workspace.Name}}</li>
                {{/if}}
                <li style="margin: 0 0 10px 30px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;" class="list-item-last">Créée le : {{formatDate AccessRequest.CreatedOn}} {{formatTime AccessRequest.CreatedOn}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><a style="background-color: transparent; color: #00627e; text-decoration: underline;" href="{{Link}}">Cliquez ici pour accéder ou modifier la demande</a></p>
            {{#if AccessRequest.IsPending}}
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">[FR] Your requests currently exceed the capacity for the number of First Aid Attendant FAA or Floor Emergency Officers FEO needed to be onsite. FAA and FEO have been advise that the maximum capacity has been reached and that the organization requires a minimum of one more volunteer to be onsite.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">[FR] There are legislative requirements for trained FAA or FEO to be on site at all times during operational hours.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">[FR] Your request is currently pending, until an FEO or FAA will make their reservation.  You will receive a confirmation when your request will be approve.</p>
            {{/if}}
        </td>
    </tr>
